      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the tip. i don't think it's blight though because there aren't really any spots or anything, just the yellowing. i read somewhere online that it might be a nitrogen deficiency... how can i tell for sure if it's that? and how do i fix the soil if that's the case?",
